body.p:
To import XML from Excel 2007-2010 (.xlsx) documents, 
      needs additional libraries from the release 3.10 of Apache POI project. Follow these steps:

download version 3.10 of the Apache POI project from http://poi.apache.org/download.html. If a newer version has been released, you
          can still find version 3.10 at http://archive.apache.org/dist/poi/release/bin/ ;

from the downloaded project locate and add the following .jar files
          in the lib directory of the
            installation folder of 
          plugin.xml
            file:



dom4j-1.6.1.jar;




poi-ooxml-3.10-FINAL-20140208.jar;




poi-ooxml-schemas-3.10-FINAL-20140208.jar;




xmlbeans-2.3.0.jar.
